    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. Do you think it's a bit too cold though? Marcus was actually really personable and we really liked him. Could we add a sentence or two that makes it feel a little more \"human\" and less like a template, without making it sound unprofessional or unprofessionaly casual? Maybe something that acknowledges the effort he put in?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
