      "content": "Subject: Your Application for Senior Dev Role at [Your Company Name]\n\nDear Marcus,\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to personally thank you for your interest in our company and the effort you put into the interview process. It's always refreshing to meet someone as talented and passionate as you are.\n\nAfter careful consideration and thorough evaluation, we regret to inform you that we have decided to move forward with another candidate for the Senior Dev position at [Your Company Name]. This decision was incredibly tough, given your impressive skills, experience, and the positive energy you brought to our team.\n\nWe genuinely appreciate the time you invested in learning more about our company and working with us during the interview process. We wish you all the best in your future endeavors and hope you find the opportunity that perfectly aligns with your unique talents and experience.\n\nThank you once again for your interest and understanding.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Job Title]\n[Your Company Name]\n[Your Contact Information]",
